          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>New York 79 Duane St</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <date>August 12, 49</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>To the <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee></p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Dr Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">I beg to enclose Ten Dollars for the amnt.<lb/> of
                                        books I bought of you; viz: one <add>תפילה</add> &amp; one
                                                  <add>חמשים</add>, and<lb/> with many thanks for
                                        the indulgence of credit</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">I remain Dr Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">Respectfully yours</p>
                              <p rend="indent(10)">
                                        <persName role="author">A Loewe</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>P. S. I should like very much to have the underneath inserted in
                                        your<lb/> valuable periodical, but as I can not afford to
                                        spend much for it,<lb/> you will oblige me by stating in a
                                        line or two the lowest you could<lb/> do it for me for the
                                        term of 1 month.</p>
                              <p rend="align(center)">
                                        <hi rend="underline">Hebrew, German, and English taught</hi>
                              </p>
                              <p><persName>Mr Adolph Loewe</persName> (brother of <persName>Dr L.
                                                  Loewe</persName> of <placeName>London</placeName>)
                                        begs<lb/> to inform his friends &amp; public in general
                                        that, he intends devoting a<lb/> few of his leisure hours to
                                        leading <hi rend="underline"><sic>privat</sic> classes</hi>
                                        in the Hebrew<lb/> German &amp; English languages either at
                                        my own residence <placeName>79 Duane St<lb/> New
                                                  York</placeName>, or at that of the pupils,,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)"><add>?</add> Terms moderate</p>
                    </body>
